Package: plotcli
Type: Package
Title: Command Line Interface Plotting in R
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2024-04-01
Author: Claas Heuer
Maintainer: Your Name <claasheuer@gmail.com>
Description: The plotcli package provides terminal-based plotting in R.
             It supports colored scatter plots, 
             line plots, bar plots, and box plots. The package allows users 
             to customize plot appearance, add titles, labels, ticks, 
             and legends, and output the plot as a text-based visualization.
